INSERT INTO `vertowp_posts` VALUES(12, 1, '2012-05-17 16:09:39', '2012-05-17 16:09:39', '<div id="vision">\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-42" title="mockup_road" src="http://localhost:8888/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/mockup_road.png" alt="" width="940" height="198" />\r\n<h1>Vision</h1>\r\n<h3 id="vision">At verto, our products are developed with a simple vision in mind...</h3>\r\n<blockquote>The first and only application our users choose to empower their work.</blockquote>\r\nThe premise behind this goal is not that we intend to create an application that forces a user to only use our software, but to create:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><b>Compelling interfaces</b> so that all of our clients will <span style="text-decoration: underline;">want</span> to use our products.</em></li>\r\n	<li><b>Integrated solutions</b> that enable users to have access to all data at their fingertips.</li>\r\n	<li><b>Customizable Modules</b> to ensure "our product" can be configured to become "your application"</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Empower the user and the rest will follow</h4>\r\nIt''s time to step away from the top-down model of application development. Although it is important to create applications with management in mind, it is imperative to remember that the data an application provides is only as useful as the information that is entered by the users. By using intuitive interfaces and user-tailored layouts, we promote better data quality and thus a more relevant application.\r\n<h4>Break interaction barriers with data transparency</h4>\r\nHow many times have you requested a deliverable only to have something completely different provided instead? Do you work in a team and have no idea what your peers are doing? We believe that these situations can be removed through the correct promotion of data transparency. Show your customers that they are a vital part of your organization. Provide them with real time updates as you enter information and give them instant feedback. Create effective teams through automated application alerts and passive data sharing. And the best part is, you can do all this while reducing your overall employee workload. Remove the veil of traditional low-tech interaction and empower your client-employee management relationships\r\n<h4>Saving one person''s time, shouldn''t cost another''s</h4>\r\nWhy should streamlining your management mean shifting load onto your employees? The answer is simple... it shouldn''t. We only design clean and effective data management technology to ensure that data duplication becomes a concept of the past all while drastically increasing the effectiveness of your administrative personnel. When it comes to information, we take the "Cost" out of your cost Benefit Analysis.\r\n<h4>Repetition means automation</h4>\r\nIf you do something once, do it well. If you do that same thing again, automate it! Whether this means creating ad-hoc reports that can be run on a schedule, or e-mailing alerts to your users, we make the computer work instead of you.\r\n<h4>Integration Everywhere</h4>\r\nAre you scared of having yet another proprietary application? Another requirement for a data clerk to ensure information stays relevant and accurate? Worry no more. All our applications are designed with inbound/outbound integration in mind. So, not only do we ensure data is up-to-date with your master record, but we also provide the means to extract this data easily from our application. Use our applications only when you want to.\r\n</div>', 'Vision', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vision', '', '', '2012-05-18 16:10:41', '2012-05-18 16:10:41', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?page_id=12', 0, 'page', '', 0);
